OL,3,CAll Scottish pensioners to receive
OL,4,Cwinter heating payment next year
OL,6,FEvery pensioner in Scotland will
OL,7,Freceive a payment for winter fuel next
OL,8,Fyear, Scottish social justice
OL,9,Fsecretary Shirley-Anne Somerville
OL,10,Fannounced, following Westminster's
OL,11,Fdecision to restrict the nationwide
OL,12,Fbenefit, ITV News Correspondent Peter
OL,13,FSmith reports
OL,15,FPensioners in Scotland will receive a
OL,16,Fwinter heating payment next year, the
OL,17,FScottish government has announced.
