OL,3,CAll Scottish pensioners to receive
OL,4,Cwinter heating payment next year
OL,6,FMinisters had been forced to delay the
OL,7,Fimplementation of a devolved pension-
OL,8,Fage winter heating payment, after the
OL,9,FUK-wide was cut for millions of people
OL,10,Fafter the Westminster government made
OL,11,Fthe benefit means-tested this year.
OL,13,FScottish social justice secretary
OL,14,FShirley-Anne Somerville announced that
OL,15,Fthe government would ensure every
OL,16,Fpensioner would receive a payment next
OL,17,Fyear.
