OL,3,CAll Scottish pensioners to receive
OL,4,Cwinter heating payment next year
OL,6,FUnder the plans, those in receipt of
OL,7,Fpension credit or other benefits and
OL,8,Fwho have received a #200 or #300
OL,9,Fpayment this year will get the same
OL,10,Fnext year through the devolved scheme.
OL,12,FAll other pensioners will receive a
OL,13,Freduced payment of #100.
