OL,3,CAll Scottish pensioners to receive
OL,4,Cwinter heating payment next year
OL,6,FAs well as widening the eligibility of
OL,7,Fthe payment, Ms Somerville also
OL,8,Fannounced a further #20 million for
OL,9,Fthe Scottish Welfare Fund and the same
OL,10,Famount for Warmer Homes Scotland in
OL,11,Fthis financial year.
OL,13,FThe Scottish government, she said, has
OL,14,Fbeen forced to "mitigate" decisions
OL,15,Fmade by the UK government, adding:
OL,16,F"There has been change, but that
OL,17,Fchange is that we are now mitigating
OL,18,Fagainst a Labour government and not a
OL,19,FTory one.
