OL,4,Cwinter heating payment next year
OL,6,F"We have not taken this decision
OL,7,Flightly, given the significant
OL,8,Fpressures on the Scottish government's
OL,9,Fbudget, but this Scottish government
OL,10,Fis determined to stay true to our
OL,11,Fvalues.
OL,13,F"On our watch, we will treat people in
OL,14,Fthis country with fairness, dignity
OL,15,Fand respect.
OL,17,F"We will not abandon older people this
OL,18,Fwinter, or indeed any winter, and we
OL,19,Fwill continue to protect our
OL,20,Fpensioners from the harsh reality of a
OL,21,FUK Labour government."
