OL,6,FThe minister was accused by Scottish
OL,7,FTory social security spokeswoman Liz
OL,8,FSmith of "hoodwinking" pensioners by
OL,9,Fmaking the announcement seem like a
OL,10,Freturn to the full payment.
OL,12,FBut Ms Somerville said: "We have
OL,13,Freturned to a universal payment for
OL,14,Fpensioners, and that is an important
OL,15,Fprinciple we are determined to hold
OL,16,Fto."
OL,18,FThe minister added that Scots will see
OL,19,Fthe benefit as "an investment in our
OL,20,Fpeople".
