OL,6,FWhile the Social Justice Secretary
OL,7,Fsparred with Labour social justice
OL,8,Fspokesman Paul O'Kane, who asked if
OL,9,Fthe increase in spending coming to
OL,10,FScotland through the Barnett formula
OL,11,Fas a result of UK government decisions
OL,12,Fhad allowed the change.
OL,14,F"I think as well as asking some
OL,15,Fquestions, which he is obviously right
OL,16,Fto do, Mr O'Kane and his party should
OL,17,Fcome here with a bit of humility and a
OL,18,Fbit of an apology for Scotland's
OL,19,Fpensioners for putting us in this
OL,20,Fposition in the first place."
