OL,6,FThe announcement was also somewhat
OL,7,Fmarred by the leaking of details of
OL,8,Fthe scheme to the press, with reports
OL,9,Femerging on Thursday morning ` hours
OL,10,Fbefore Ms Somerville addressed the
OL,11,FScottish Parliament.
OL,13,FAs a result, she apologised to
OL,14,FPresiding Officer Alison Johnstone,
OL,15,Fwho cut the statement short to allow
OL,16,Fmore time for MSPs to question the
OL,17,Fminister.
